---
import CtaButton from "./CtaButton.astro";
import SatisfiedCounter from "./SatisfiedCounter.astro";
---

<section class="bg-[#fff] px-[5%] py-12 md:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <p class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">
      SO HERE'S THE DEAL
    </p>

    <h2 class="mb-6 font-heading text-2xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-heading text-foreground md:text-4xl">
      You're not just buying a swipe file. You're stepping into a system.
    </h2>

    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#333]">
      A system that will allow you to find winning supplement ads, reverse-engineer them into replicable profiles, and generate unlimited creative variations with AI.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#333]">
      Which means you'll finally have the creative firepower to scale your supplement ads profitably — without the guesswork, without the burnout, and without the wasted ad spend.
    </p>

    <ul class="mb-8 flex flex-col gap-3">
      <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cta-green">
          <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[#fff]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">
          500+ winning supplement ads at your fingertips — organized and ready to replicate
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cta-green">
          <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[#fff]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">
          AI workflows that generate dozens of scroll-stopping creatives in minutes
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cta-green">
          <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[#fff]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">
          a creative system that never runs dry — beat ad fatigue permanently
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-8 text-lg font-bold leading-relaxed text-foreground">
      As soon as you click that button below, you're making a decision to stop guessing at creatives — and start producing winners on demand.
    </p>

    <CtaButton text="Get Supplement Ads Now" variant="green" />
    <SatisfiedCounter variant="light" />
  </div>
</section>
